#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:3
msgid "Currencies"
msgstr "Divisas"

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:5
msgid ""
"This section allows adding as many currencies as wanted. It is a "
"multilanguage field with a symbol that will be used in invoices, balance "
"movements, etc."
msgstr "Esta sección permite añadir tantas divisas como se desee. Es un campo multilingüe con un símbolo que se utilizará en facturas, movimientos de saldo, etc."

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:8
msgid "These IvozProvider elements have an assigned currency:"
msgstr "Estos elementos de IvozProvider tienen una divisa asignada:"

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:11
msgid "Brand"
msgstr "Marca"

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:11
msgid "Used as default currency for all underlying items that have currency."
msgstr "Utilizado como divisa predeterminada para todos los elementos subyacentes que tienen divisa."

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:15
msgid "Client"
msgstr "Cliente"

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:14
msgid ""
"Chosen currency will be used in price calculation, invoices, invoice's "
"fixed costs, balance movements and remaining money operations of this "
"client."
msgstr "La divisa elegida se utilizará en el cálculo de precios, facturas, costos fijos de la factura, movimientos de saldo y operaciones de dinero restantes de este cliente."

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:19
msgid "Carrier"
msgstr "Operador"

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:18
msgid ""
"Chosen currency will be used in cost calculation, balance movements and "
"remaining money operations of this carrier."
msgstr "La divisa elegida se utilizará en el cálculo de costos, movimientos de saldo y operaciones de dinero restantes de este operador."

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:22
msgid "Destination rate"
msgstr "Tarifa de destino"

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:22
msgid "All rates within a destination rate will assume this currency."
msgstr "Todas las tarifas dentro de una tarifa de destino asumirán esta divisa."

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:26
msgid "Rating plan"
msgstr "Plan de precios"

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:25
msgid "All destination rates grouped in a rating plan **must** use this currency."
msgstr "Todas las tarifas de destino agrupadas en un plan de precios **deben** usar esta divisa."

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:28
msgid ""
"It is important to take into account notes below before using this "
"feature:"
msgstr "Es importante tener en cuenta las notas a continuación antes de usar esta función:"

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:30
msgid "Rating plans **must** only group destination rates using its currency."
msgstr "Los planes de precios **deben** agrupar solo tarifas de destino que usen su divisa."

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:32
msgid "Clients and carriers **must** only use rating plans using its currency."
msgstr "Los clientes y operadores **deben** usar solo planes de precios que usen su divisa."

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:34
msgid ""
"Some backend checks avoid some of previous misconfigurations, but not all"
" of them: **use this feature carefully**."
msgstr "Algunas verificaciones en el backend evitan algunas de las configuraciones incorrectas anteriores, pero no todas: **use esta función con cuidado**."

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:36
msgid ""
"**There is no currency conversion involved**: call cost will be "
"calculated in carrier's currency, call price will be calculated in "
"client's currency."
msgstr "**No hay conversión de divisas involucrada**: el costo de la llamada se calculará en la divisa del operador, el precio de la llamada se calculará en la divisa del cliente."

#: ../../administration_portal/platform/currencies.rst:39
msgid "LCR routes involving carriers with different currencies are not supported."
msgstr "Las rutas LCR que involucran operadores con diferentes divisas no son compatibles."

